## SPECIFIC INSTRUCTIONS

### When Updating Text:
- Keep all existing HTML tags (`<h1>`, `<p>`, `<a>`, etc.)
- Preserve all class names and IDs
- Maintain link structures (only change link text, not href)
- Keep button elements intact (only change button text)
- Don't add new HTML elements unless specifically instructed

### When Adding Images (Later):
- Only update `src` attributes
- Keep all image `alt` attributes
- Maintain image wrapper structures
- Don't change image dimensions or classes

### For Lists:
- Keep `<ul>` or `<ol>` structures
- Only update `<li>` text content
- Maintain any icons or checkmarks

### For Links:
- Update link text only
- Keep `href` attributes unless specifically told to change
- Preserve `target` and other attributes

